Package: ecodive
Type: Package
Title: Microbiome Algorithms Implemented in 'C'
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-07-31
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Daniel P.", "Smith",
      email   = "dansmith01@gmail.com",
      role    = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2479-2044")),
    person(
      "Alkek Center for Metagenomics and Microbiome Research", 
      role = c("cph", "fnd") ))
Description:
    Computes alpha- and beta- diversity metrics (including 'UniFrac'). 
    Also parses newick trees into a 'phylo' object and rarefies abundance
    matrices. Algorithms are parallelized across all CPU cores by default.
URL: https://cmmr.github.io/ecodive/, https://github.com/cmmr/ecodive
BugReports: https://github.com/cmmr/ecodive/issues
